modules.description: Provides functions for parsing, formatting, and manipulating date-time values, including timezone conversions and duration calculations. Works with custom data types such as date, time, and datetime, along with duration and timezone representations. Enables precise scheduling, log timestamp analysis, and time zone-aware data aggregation.

Parses time and date strings into structured representations, including durations, time spans, and datetime objects with optional time zone support. It handles specific formats for hours-minutes-seconds, date-time combinations, and time spans. Functions return either results or raise exceptions, enabling precise error handling or direct usage in workflows requiring time parsing.
